      pivot_paths: 'Analyst → senior analyst → manager → senior manager → director → VP is the corporate ladder. PM → senior PM → group PM → director PM → VP product is the product ladder. Many pivot through consulting (entry $90-120K, exit to industry director-level roles). Founder/operator path increasingly viable as alternative to corporate ladder.'
