      demographics: 'Finance still skews male, especially in IB + PE + HF (~80% men in senior positions). Corporate accounting + financial planning more gender-balanced. Black + Latino representation low in IB + asset management (~3-5% combined at MD level). Significant industry diversity initiatives but slow change.',
      entry_picks: { hs: [], cert: [], associate: ['accountant'], bachelor: ['accountant', 'analystfin', 'finadvisor', 'auditor', 'actuary', 'realestate', 'underwriter'], graduate: ['analystfin', 'finadvisor', 'cfo'], doctoral: [], professional: [] },
      journals: ['The Wall Street Journal', 'Financial Times', 'Bloomberg', 'CFA Institute Journal'],
