      hiring_portals: ['usajobs.gov (federal)', 'state-specific portals (CA: calcareers.ca.gov, etc.)', 'governmentjobs.com (local + state)', 'Foreign Service: state.gov'],
      pivot_paths: 'Federal → consulting → contractor is a well-trodden post-government pivot for $200-400K total comp jumps. State/local → federal possible with strong specialization. Many government scientists/engineers pivot to industry. Lifetime federal employees often retire to consulting or board roles.'
