      salary_arc: 'Entry: junior designer + production assistant $40-55K. Mid: senior designer + UX designer $85-130K, journalist $50-75K. Senior: design director + executive editor $120-180K. Top: showrunner + creative director $200K-$1M+. Many fine artists + musicians earn <$30K from primary craft.',
      growth_story: 'UX/product design strong demand. Game industry cyclical with major 2022-2024 layoffs. Animation + VFX consolidating + offshoring. Journalism contracting (especially local). Podcasting + creator economy growing but income concentrated at top. Architecture + interior design steady.',
