      intro: 'Law, public safety + corrections spans attorneys, paralegals, judges, mediators, police, firefighters, corrections officers, federal LE, security professionals. ~6M jobs. Attorney income bimodal ($60-80K public interest, $200K+ big law). Public safety roles middle-class with strong benefits + pension + early retirement.',
